text: Murray Cheater (26 January 1947 - 4 August 2020) was a New Zealand athlete. He competed in the men's hammer throw at the 1976 Summer Olympics. He was born in Auckland. Cheater died on 4 August 2020 at the age of 73. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:2020 deaths Category:New Zealand athletes Category:Olympians for New Zealand Category:Hammer throwers Category:Sportspeople from Auckland
